name: Kathy_Ireland_Tall_Wood_Metal_Etagere
reviews: Purchased this for extra bathroom storage. It is made of very thin hollow wood shelving, much like model airplane material. Assembled, it is not very sturdy and very lightweight. I like how it looks if you don't touch it.
